CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "FROGS Step Out in Traditional Style...Loquacious - Miss Miriam Bush, Mrs. Bern Milai and Howard Riekmond sit on a table and chat while they enjoy refreshments at the annual Frog's picnic, this year at South Park Lodge. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Miriam Bush, Bern Milai, and Howard Reikmond at FROGS picnic, South Park lodge
